  "subject": "Fix: Remove sphinx-toolbox and fix RTD build failure",
  "commit_message": "Fix: Remove sphinx-toolbox and fix RTD build failure\n\nRemove sphinx_toolbox.collapse from conf.py extensions and sphinx-toolbox\nfrom requirements-docs.txt and upper-constraints.onap.txt. The extension\nis unused in this repository (no collapse directives in RST content)\nand sphinx-toolbox 4.1.2 is incompatible with Sphinx 9.x, breaking all\nRTD builds.\n\nAlso update examples/sphinx/.readthedocs.yaml to ubuntu-24.04 and\nPython 3.13 (RTD ubuntu-20.04 deprecation, June 2026).\n\nAdd documentation guide for affected repositories.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: Ibc7648b90bf345bc4df36ad53aa34af83c4543c3\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
